{"type": "article", "id": 2932, "title": "防止液体打翻的托盘", "description": "", "date": "2014-10-20T08:34:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 4, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232411HneR71BEo4PpsJay.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t生活中，不慎打翻各种液体的窘况偶有发生，尤其是在公众场合，免不了出现尴尬局面。近日，美国设计品牌 FINELL 就带来了一款可以解决这一问题的小作品 GRIP 。它实际上是一个托盘，特别之处在于在基础的托盘之上加入了有弹性的橡胶材料，可以将各种液体容器捆绑在托盘上，避免其倾泻或者打翻，提供长方形与圆形两种选择。长方形款定价 295 美元，圆形款定价 395 美元，<a href=\"http://finell.co/products/grip/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052324095P82Bbd9nL1gl0jE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.575\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232410MeqoirtBFXTwHY2N.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.575\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232410nr5HSLXWCykAKD1P.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.575\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232410IpxVwq2c1t6QTPev.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.575\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}